scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 296-431 contain the full text of the Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, including all its parts and the signatures. The Schedule begins at line 296 with the heading 'SCHEDULE to the Master Agreement' and continues through the various parts (Termination Provisions, Tax Representations, Agreement to Deliver Documents, Miscellaneous, Other Provisions) until the execution block at the end. This span excludes the standard pre-printed Master Agreement and any annexes, focusing solely on the Schedule as requested.
